What is Llama?

Llama (Large Language Model Meta AI) is an open-source Large Language Model (LLM) developed by Meta (Facebook).

It is similar to:

ChatGPT (OpenAI)
Gemini (Google)
Claude (Anthropic)
Mistral AI

But Llama is open-source, so you can download and run it yourself.

Simple Definition

Llama is an AI brain that understands and generates human language.

